, transport og montering, slik at folkemuseet overtar \u00abByen\u00bb uten egne omkostninger."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "kultur"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "db1e5154a837b66775a851f60b46993f83e56c0b66b48484a8148f16b70f7583"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2015-11-10T00:25:13.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "H\u00e5kon Blekens \u00abByen\u00bb er kommet p\u00e5 plass p\u00e5 Sverresborg Tr\u00f8ndelag folkemuseum."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/kultur/article10373080.ece/oss26d/ALTERNATES/w980-default/EB_Bleken_Sverresborg_03.jpg"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/2e8252cfc660a429286f2790891279a1bb65f264.jpg?5963180f"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": ["- Det er blitt et monument -adressa.no", "En overgang", "Mye tid"]}, {"field": "id", "value": "2e8252cfc660a429286f2790891279a1bb65f264"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["anmeldelser", "det skjer", "film", "musikk", "tv", "museum", "scene", "spill"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "anmeldelser,det skjer,film,musikk,tv,museum,scene,spill"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": "kultur"}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "law-government-and-politics"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["million kroner", "kunstverket", "byen"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["decom", "pr\u00f8ven transport", "sverresborg tr\u00f8ndelag", "torunn herje", "trondhjems bys vel", "selskabet for trondhjems bys vel", "byen", "bytorget", "vitenskapsmuseet"]}, {"field": "kw-location", "value": "trondheim"}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-person", "value": ["nils henrik eggen", "h\u00e5kon bleken"]}, {"field": "kw-taxonomy", "value": "kultur"}, {"field": "og-image", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/kultur/article10373080.ece/oss26d/ALTERNATES/w980-default/EB_Bl